  <acronym>ECHOKIDS</acronym>
  <official_title>Echocardiography in Kids Intensive Care Decision Support - is Focused Echocardiography Superior to Pressure Derived Measurements at Predicting Fluid Responsiveness in Critically Ill Children?</official_title>
